RelatedSentence: ( MENAFN ) Hamad Medical Corporation ( HMC ) has signed an agreement with Community College of Qatar ( CCQ ) to raise healthcare awareness and boost career opportunities , according to Arabian Business .
The two parties will collaborate on the design , development and implementation of an associate applied science degree in health information management ( HIM ) through the agreement .
The agreement will help ensure sufficient capacity to meet the complex , highly specialized healthcare needs of Qatar 's population .
